metadata.name: Bink Sake
metadata.description:
Bink sake, most emotional scene in which 'Brook' and his crew sing the song for the last time and everybody dies except him.
Fan art of one of my favorite characters in the ONE PIECE anime.
spent more than 2 days on this.

3D

Made in Blender.

resolution: 2160 x 2160

Desktop wallpaper will be provided.
